So, let's talk
about that dragon.

829
01:03:08,273 --> 01:03:09,876
Oh, gods, Dad.

830
01:03:10,010 --> 01:03:11,878
I'm-I'm-I'm so sorry.

831
01:03:11,911 --> 01:03:13,245
