935
01:08:43,876 --> 01:08:45,912
-What...
-Toothless, no!

936
01:08:45,979 --> 01:08:46,745
Stop. It's okay.

937
01:08:46,778 --> 01:08:49,748
She's a friend. She's a friend.

938
01:08:53,953 --> 01:08:57,190
Toothless, Astrid.
Astrid, Toothless.

939
01:08:57,323 --> 01:09:00,492
